"2022-06-30T19:32:24.687","modifiedByFull":"Rauston, Gustav","remark":"Commercial agreement to not bill Mollendo, Pampilla and Callao as interim (as per actual CP interim port clause) and instead bill with additional lumpsums resulting in considerable lower PnL/TCE"},{"modifiedDate":"2022-06-08T14:46:13.297","modifiedByFull":"Ervasti, Josh","remark":"Interim ports added x 3 w/ deviation bunkers etc etc"},{"modifiedDate":"2022-05-24T17:28:11.74","modifiedByFull":"Ervasti, Josh","remark":"voyage was generated without add\u0027l port La Pampilla"},{"modifiedDate":"2022-05-20T20:01:03.17","modifiedByFull":"Ervasti, Josh","remark":"Canal costs adjusted and prebooking split 50/50 - cleaning costs adjusted"},{"modifiedDate":"2022-05-18T13:01:12.267","modifiedByFull":"Ervasti, Josh","remark":"bunkers on ballast passage less than expected"},{"modifiedDate":"2022-05-17T15:07:04.89","modifiedByFull":"Ervasti, Josh","remark":"2 days dem added at 28kpdy"}],"offhireList":[],"tcNumber":null,"tcOutIdEncrypted":null,"tcReletDetail":null}